OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCleverly promises to praise
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpolice in public           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, New Home Secretary James Cleverly has  
OL,6, told UK police chiefs he will praise   
OL,7, them in public and criticise them in   
OL,8, private.                               
OL,10,FMr Cleverly was addressing a major     
OL,11,Fpolicing conference in London after    
OL,12,Ftaking up the role of home secretary   
OL,13,Fthis week.                             
OL,15,FLast week his predecessor, Suella      
OL,16,FBraverman, wrote an article in The     
OL,17,FTimes accusing officers of "playing    
OL,18,Ffavourites" when policing protests.    
OL,20,FMrs Braverman was sacked on Monday.    
